overview: "Seether will play the Vicennial album in sequence for one night only at the Ace of Spades in Sacramento, California on Oct. 7. The event will be an Aftershock after party after opening night of the upcoming festival.  For those who can't make that show, Seether also have a livestreamed event that fans will be able to catch on Nov. 11 through a partnership with the Moment House premium digital platform. There will be shows at 6PM PT, 6PM GMT and 6PM JST where fans are able to vote for that time zoneâ€™s 10-song set. Additionally, the band will be appearing live for Q&A sessions and virtual meet and greets.
title: Seether - Vicennial Live Stream
